flowchart TD
    A[Load songs from data/songs.csv] --> B[Convert each song to a feature vector]
    U[User profile / preferences] --> C[Convert profile to a target vector]
    B --> N[Normalize features to 0-1<br/>rescale tempo BPM]
    C --> N
    N --> D[Euclidean distance: target vs each song]
    D --> E[Similarity = 1 - distance / max distance]
    E --> F[Add bonuses:<br/>genre match, mood match, acoustic preference]
    F --> G[Sort by score, highest first<br/>tie-break on title]
    G --> H[Take top K]
    H --> I[Show ranked recommendations + reasons]
